Path: This week in Nu #18
Content:
Ho ho ho happy holidays!
andrasio continues work on the subcrate refactor (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1128] #1128
)
jonathandturner fixed an issue with utf-8 support (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1126] #1126
)
jonathandturner also added a new 
``$nu``
 variable to replace 
``$nu:path``
 and related. Additionally, 
``ps``
 now has a new memory usage column (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1112] #1112
)
notryanb helped update our docs with the new 
``$nu``
 variable (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1125] #1125
)
quebin31 fixed calling 
``cd``
 by itself (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1124] #1124
)
thegedge fixed a performance bug with pipelines between external commands (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1108] #1108
)
